793. Health Technol Assess. 2019 Jul;23(35):1-48. doi: 10.3310/hta23350.

Tranexamic acid to improve functional status in adults with spontaneous 
intracerebral haemorrhage: the TICH-2 RCT.

Sprigg N(1)(2), Flaherty K(1), Appleton JP(1), Al-Shahi Salman R(3), Bereczki 
D(4), Beridze M(5), Ciccone A(6), Collins R(7), Dineen RA(8)(9), Duley L(10), 
Egea-Guerrero JJ(11), England TJ(12), Karlinski M(13), Krishnan K(1)(2), Laska 
