I(19), Robinson TG(20), Roffe C(21), Peters N(22), Scutt P(1), Thanabalan J(23), 
Werring D(24)(25), Whynes D(26), Woodhouse L(1), Bath PM(1)(2).

Author information:
(1)Stroke Trials Unit, Division of Clinical Neuroscience, University of 
Nottingham, Nottingham, UK.
(2)Stroke, Nottingham University Hospitals NHS Trust, Nottingham, UK.
(3)Centre for Clinical Brain Sciences, University of Edinburgh, Edinburgh, UK.
